Tagaytay, Philippines 🇵🇭 

Come check out this breathtaking vacation/holiday retreat for many local Filipinos.

Tagaytay is perched on a ridge about 2000 feet above sea-level overlooking a volcanic caldera called Taal Volcano in the province of Cavite.
